DIGEST
SB 8 Original 2026 Regular Session Price
Participating employers in the Municipal Employees' Retirement System of Louisiana
(MERS) are enumerated in present law, either by name or by class of employers.
Proposed law adds the Louisiana Asset Management Pool as a participating employer in
MERS.
Effective upon signature of governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
(Adds R.S. 11:1732(14)(a)(xiv))
